Thanks for applying to the Revenue Technology Specialist (RTS) program at ULEM. We're excited you're taking this step.

WHAT HAPPENS NEXT

Please complete the skills assessment. This takes about 45 to 60 minutes and is a required step in the application process.

Start the assessment here:
https://www.ondemandassessment.com/link/index/JB-3S80N5PVZ?u=37591

Use the same email address you used on the application form. That is how we match your scores back to your file.

Once we have reviewed your application and assessment, someone from our team will reach out within 5 to 7 business days.

PROGRAM REMINDER

- 10 weeks, Mon to Wed in-person (10 AM to 4 PM), Thu and Fri remote
- 100% free. Wraparound support is available based on individual need.
- Cohort 1 starts May 18, 2026

Questions? Reply to this email or reach us at programs@ulem.org.

We'll be in touch.

The RTS Team at ULEM
